<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>DealHub - Best Deals & Offers</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#f5f7fa;
color:#222;
}

header{
background:#081b3a;
padding:15px 5%;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
position:sticky;
top:0;
z-index:1000;
}

.logo{
font-size:30px;
font-weight:bold;
color:#ffb400;
}

nav a{
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
margin-left:20px;
}

.hero{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#081b3a,#0d6efd);
padding:80px 5%;
color:white;
}

.hero-content{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.hero-text{
max-width:550px;
}

.hero-text h1{
font-size:60px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero-text span{
color:#ffb400;
}

.hero-text p{
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.8;
margin-bottom:25px;
}

.btn{
background:#ffb400;
padding:14px 30px;
text-decoration:none;
color:black;
font-weight:bold;
border-radius:8px;
}

.hero-image img{
width:450px;
max-width:100%;
}

.section-title{
text-align:center;
font-size:40px;
margin:70px 0 40px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">DealHub</div>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">Categories</a>
<a href="#">Top Deals</a>
<a href="#">Blog</a>
<a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-content">

<div class="hero-text">
<h1>Best Deals, <span>Best Choices!</span></h1>

<p>
Find top quality products from Amazon & Flipkart
